    "The evaluation results are summarized in Table 1.",
    "The study's results show that ReqGPT outperforms both the baseline LLM and GPT-4 in overall mean score performance across the measured criteria.",
    "ReqGPT achieved the highest similarity score at 77% with a moderate interquartile range (IQR) of 17% (69-86%), indicating a consistent evaluation across all nine criteria.",
    "GPT-4 followed with a similarity score of 69% and a slightly narrower IQR of 13% (62-75%), reflecting a slightly smaller variability in output quality compared to ReqGPT.",
